snippet.title: Why is Mr Beast getting cancelled?
snippet.description:
#MrBeast #SquidGame #XyleGetsReal

Sat down and discussed on why this current cancelation of @MrBeast. From giving away 10k turkeys to his Squid Game recreation of the games. We went over the the Vice article and what Hwang Dong-Hyuk (the creator of Squid Game) thought about YouTubers recreating his series that took him 12 yrs to create.

Please send no hate to anyone mentioned in this live. We can be better than that!!!

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

0:00 Intro
8:09 Hello, rules and what's up
14:59 Kavos video
33:32 The Vice article
39:51 Reading the transcript from ET Canada video below
43:33 Final thoughts and discussion
54:56 Outro

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@Kavos 
"HOW COULD MR BEAST DO THIS!?" - This Is Absolute INSANITY
https://youtu.be/vSDNVofLt6c

Vice article about Mr Beast's video
https://www.vice.com/en/article/v7dd7j/mr-beasts-squid-game-ripoff-is-exactly-the-kind-of-video-youtube-rewards

ET Canada
YouTuber's 'Squid Game' Gets Creator's Stamp Of Approval
https://youtu.be/ZyfRrENaBMM
